{"title":"想起松潘草地","authors":["殷常青"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起松潘草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷常青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个温暖的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起松潘草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起那些沼泽、泥泞和高寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起一群灰色的绑腿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一双双朴实坚定的草鞋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草地上，一步、一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天幸福的雨露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样踩出来的么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个结实的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样走出来的么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起松潘草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样是一个夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空飘着大雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七根火柴一个战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站着站得多么直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团光亮，让整个中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受到了他的体温"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让整个人民的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质地坚韧了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论风怎样刮雨怎样淋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他仍然和60年前一样年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像松潘草地青青的小草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长势起伏一闪一亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然无力到达的地方很多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然深入草地的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经成为草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但挺立的姿态旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有另一个挺立的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不回头的足音后面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总跟着另一个不回头的足音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛一支挺进的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共和国的旗杆上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上升，上升……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起松潘草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七根火柴一团光亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总在眼前晃动……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}